data.description:
Welcome to 8266 S Fillmore Way, located in the charming city of Centennial, Colorado. This stunning real estate gem offers a combination of elegance, comfort, and an excellent location for those seeking a well-rounded lifestyle. 

As you step into this home, you are immediately greeted by an inviting and spacious living area that boasts an abundance of natural light. 

The residence offers two generously sized bedrooms. The master suite comes with an en-suite bathroom.

Centennial, Colorado, is known for its quality school system, beautiful parks, and a plethora of recreational opportunities. Located in close proximity to major highways and public transportation, residents of 8266 S Fillmore Way enjoy easy access to the greater Denver area. 

In addition to the convenient location, Centennial offers an array of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Southglenn Mall and Park Meadows Mall are just a short drive away, providing a variety of retail stores and popular restaurants.

Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional property in Centennial, Colorado. Schedule your private tour today and experience the contemporary style and comfortable living that 8266 S Fillmore Way has to offer.
